  TutorialSteps:
  - Message: Welcome to the tutorial!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: The combat in Realmrover is turn-based.
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: You may use as many abilities as you like in one turn as long as you
      have enough energy. Enemies will only use one Ability per turn.
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Your energy, along with your health, are shown under your character.
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: When you are finished. Click the "End Turn" button to end your turn
      and gain some energy. Try it!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 1
  - Message: 'Well done! Your Abilities are shown at the bottom of the screen. Hover
      over them to read their description. '
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: To activate an Ability, click it. Or use your Keyboard by pressing the
      corresponding number. Activate Smite!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 94b32e335699d414da494e62556a5191, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Good job! Smite deals direct damage. Useful if you want to defeat your
      enemies!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Unfortunately, enemies too can deal direct damage which is why you need
      to defend yourself. Activate Shield Block to absorb some damage!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1c667f69d64372d4186a43125b15b1e1, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Good job! Your Absorb amount is indicated on your Health Bar.
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: 'Some Abilities deal their damage over a number of turns. Activate Holy
      Slash! '
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f6aaebaa4fb5c2849bee9b93ce9f73ba, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Good job! You can also recover some missing Health by using a Healing
      Ability. Activate Prayer!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 715e2cb08c1944a479f9437f4d6b0bb4, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Good job! Some Abilities are more potent under certain conditions! Activate
      Shield Charge!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5ac9daafa3a069549b36311cad4c1d85, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Good job! Here is another one! Activate Heaven's Wrath!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ab9663710eee0a0408334fdc3c450f87, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: We are almost done. Your next Ability carries a penalty. Use it smartly!
      Go on, do not be afraid. Try it!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 80c0c0200a7604c4b83ce9a53588c2a4, type: 2}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
  - Message: Well done! This is the end of this tutorial. Good luck on your adventures!
    WaitForSkill: {fileID: 0}
    WaitForEndOfTurn: 0
